INSTALLATION!!

sudo apt install (package name)
sudo apt install nmap -y

------REMOVE-----------------
step.1
sudo apt remove (package name)
sudo apt remove nmap
sudo apt autoremove -y or sudo apt purge --remove nmap*
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
step.2 
sudo apt remove (package name)*
sudo apt remove nmap*
